name: BootPress
tagline: A starter WordPress theme for developers built on Bootstrap.
body:
### BootPress
BootPress is a WordPress theme for developers, built on Bootstrap.

To get started, clone BootPress into your `wp-content/themes`:

```
$ cd path/to/wordpress/wp-content/themes
$ git clone git@github.com:copterlabs/bootpress.git
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
